{
  "texts": [
    "However, they have many limitations, including hallucinations and outdated training data, which can lead to \"unprofessional and unstable\" responses to medical questions 9, 10.",
    "Retraining these models is costly; therefore, improving the accuracy of LLM responses to breast cancer care questions at a minimal cost remains a significant research challenge 19, 20.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, this is the first study to use RAG technology to improve the response of LLMs to breast cancer care.",
    "Previous studies have explored RAG technology in the medical field 21, 22, showing significant improvements in LLM performance.",
    "As technology advances, tools such as LangChain and GraphRAG and the use of RAG technology in medicine could become easier in the future 23."
  ]
}